---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy: NeoPasture"
  description="How NeoPasture handles the email address you provide when you join the waitlist."
>
  <Header />
  <main id="main">
    <section class="privacy">
      <h1>Privacy</h1>
      <p>NeoPasture collects only the email address you provide when you join the waitlist.</p>
      <p>
        We use it to let you know when NeoPasture launches and to share occasional updates about
        that launch. We do not sell or share your email with third parties.
      </p>
      <p>
        NeoPasture is not yet connected to a third-party email service. Once it is, this page will
        be updated to name that provider.
      </p>
      <p>
        If you have questions about your data, or want it removed, contact us at
        <a href="mailto:hello@neopasture.com">hello@neopasture.com</a>.
      </p>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .privacy {
    padding: var(--space-8) var(--page-margin);
    max-width: var(--page-width);
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .privacy h1 {
    font-size: var(--font-h1);
  }

  .privacy p {
    margin-top: var(--space-5);
    max-width: var(--measure);
  }
</style>
